Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:33.87,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:I don't wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:37.08,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:39.91,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  reason as against emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:44.65,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  l've gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:48.08,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:All my efforts will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:51.04,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Endless desire,like a haunting refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:54.44,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:Such a pain,the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.90,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:There is a way E:To change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:00:58.42,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:01.77,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:So what if I sing off-key,who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.85,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Not good at drawing,no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:08.65,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:10.34,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Overcome myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:10.34,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:Overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:13.63,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:"A Ahole New World God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:16.50,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:I'll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:17.86,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:I know you're hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:20.86,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:To be a knight D:To be a light L:For you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:21.70,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.66,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:No more fears D:No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:24.02,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Everything will work out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:26.20,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  That's "God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:28.52,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Don't get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:30.82,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  This is not real love but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.48,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:I'll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:36.69,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:Whatever happens in my life,turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:39.70,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Remember,no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:39.84,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:Every end leads to a new beginning of rhe next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:42.55,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Try to make my life complete,trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:45.01,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:51.28,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Don't look back,carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:52.89,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}C:Be yourself... Be happy... It's your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:54.14,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  "God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:57.71,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Find your love... Find your way... For your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:11.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:33.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不願讓機會溜掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:37.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  為什麼會被剝奪自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:39.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  與感性相對比的理性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:44.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不得不克服失望感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:48.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  所有努力決不會白費
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:51.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  就像沒有終點的慾望翻覆於心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:54.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  理想與現實之間的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  應該有改變時間的方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:00:58.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  對 就這麼交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:01.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不固定音程去唱歌 也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  糟糕的繪畫也無所謂 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:08.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我為了唯一的信念而前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:10.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我要勝過我自己  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:10.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  你要勝過你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:13.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  "只有神知道的全新世界"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:16.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我一直都是你的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:17.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我知道你在痛苦著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:20.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  成為騎士,成為照耀你的明燈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:21.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我們會就這樣閃耀下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  已經不再恐懼 不再流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:24.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  一切都會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:26.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  這便是"只有神知道"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:28.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:30.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  這不是現實中的戀愛 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  為了你 我願意做任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:36.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  無論我的生命中發生什麼事 都會翻過嶄新的一頁長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:39.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不要忘記 我不想被任何人所評說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:39.84,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  一切的終結都通往著下一個舞台的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:42.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  理解走過的人生 相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:45.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  變得更強 做到最好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:51.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不回首過去 持續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:52.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  活出你自己的幸福... 因為這是你自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:54.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  "只有神知道"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:57.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  找到愛... 找到道路... 為了你自己的人生
